analysis: The agent included an unsupported argument "include_legal_requirements" in the ERA function call, deviating from the required parameters and causing a mismatch with the expected function signature.

The agent failed to include the required "work_focus": false parameter in the TMA_S function call, resulting in a parameter mismatch and preventing the function call from matching the expected format.

The agent used the correct function ("RND") but incorrectly passed the parameter "loud rattling noise" instead of the required "loud rattling" for "noise_level." This mismatch caused the evaluator to not recognize the function call as valid.

The agent called the correct function (CES_E) but failed to include required parameters "include_attachment": true and "encryption_level": "high" in its arguments, resulting in an incomplete function call that did not match the expected specification.

The agent incorrectly added the "provide_indoor_options" parameter to the HWA function call, which is not part of the expected or available function signature, causing a mismatch and function call failure.

The agent added unsupported parameters ("pattern_detection", "include_visualization", "focus_on_physical_training") to the ETTP function call instead of only passing the required "training_routine_data" argument, resulting in a function signature mismatch and no matching call found.

The agent incorrectly included an unsupported argument "consider_temperature": true in the CRBOW function call, deviating from the required parameters. Only the "city" parameter should have been provided as per the tool specification.

The agent incorrectly set the include_age_group_analysis, include_location_analysis, and include_device_usage parameters to true instead of false as required by the expected function call, resulting in a parameter mismatch with the expected API input.

The agent added unsupported arguments ("include_population_estimates" and "data_format") to the OBD_F function call, which expects only "zone_identifier". This caused a mismatch and no valid function call was matched by the evaluator.

The agent failed to include the "offers_gluten_free": true parameter in the VFRS function call, omitting a key user requirement for gluten-free options. This resulted in an incomplete and incorrect tool invocation.

The agent failed to include the required parameter "include_indoor_suggestions" (expected as false) in its WWC function call, resulting in a mismatch with the function signature expected by the evaluator.
The agent incorrectly used "technology startup" as the industry parameter instead of "technology," leading to a mismatch with the expected function call format for TR_T and thus causing the failure.
